| **Group 2 — Signature** | Tampered payload, tampered sig, missing sig | ❌ **0 of 3** | **Entire group missing.** No signature validation exists |
| **Group 3 — Deterministic Routing** | Sorted UUID order, identical routing across runs | ✅ **1 of 2** | [test_dispatch_determinism](file:///c:/Users/sergi/colony/backend/col/engine/coe-kernel/tests/test_event_bus.py#104-128) covers sorted order. **Cross-run determinism test missing** |
| **Group 4 — Dead Letter** | Exception → DLQ, Timeout → DLQ, Failure reason recorded | ⚠️ **2 of 3** | Exception and reason tested. **Timeout → DLQ missing** (no timeout implemented) |
